  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for sustainable finance questionnaire development&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;The Paris Agreement recognized the role of finance in enabling the transition to a low-carbon and resilient economy. Retail investors have the potential to help solve this problem: They own 40% of financial assets in Europe (securities, funds, pensions, bank deposits), and over 60% declare they want to make a difference with their money, notably on climate. This grant will support the adoption of climate change mitigating solutions through climate finance-specific retail banking questionnaires, guidelines, and a robo-advisory solution in the European Union.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
